{"tid":1653160,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[偽黃絲]龍門冰室一定係富臨旗下","createTime":"2019-10-14T03:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T09:33:34.000Z","uid":165381,"like":7,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"f933d28c3b8eb958ef18b5f13be3ddd44d94185b","tid":1653160,"uid":165381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"我有朋友係佢姓張嗰個老闆既朋友<br />\n姓張嗰條友係一個資深會計師<br />\n日日笑9你地， 小恩小惠搞爆左個垃圾場<br />\n唔好俾佢張 BR(商業登記證)就呃咗啦 <br />\n每間鋪都會有佢自己嘅br <br />\n佢貼嗰張br 根本唔代表啲咩<br />\n仲要del 咗呢張IG相， 根本身有屎<br />\n見到富臨出事就扮割蓆<br />\n仲喺度賺盡你地黃絲＄， 嘔心<br />\n<br />\n龍門冰室下一步就係搞上市， <br />\n到時你哋就睇到姓張條仆街同富臨楊維既關係<br />\n不過到時已經太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkgdHrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkgdHrL.png&h=6d0c1089&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/14/111124_256add554e6bb2088c1df9cbf3b563c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F14%2F111124_256add554e6bb2088c1df9cbf3b563c4.png&h=5821e0f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6eaca3a9f86ae8f1b3fe3af52c63a539c84d784","tid":1653160,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45d7e04022c2037bdc32fd6917d0b2d64b4539b","tid":1653160,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\